{"tid":2280644,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本愛媛縣貓島 (青島)發生緊急事件：島上貓咪突然消失不見了","createTime":"2020-11-10T15:21:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T15:51:23.000Z","uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ba2e647733c83dc0bf7c64244efc2439e1fe018f","tid":2280644,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T15:21:59.000Z","msg":"經常為各位愛貓之人提供愛媛縣貓島最新情報的版主「猫の島青島物語」，在剛剛的11月10日晚上，發布了一篇緊急文章，題目為「緊急事態！很多貓咪不見了。」，內容講述島上的貓咪因為不明的原因而消失，令人相當擔心。<br />\n<br />\n我在11月10日前往了青島。<br />\n在5日之前，島友「貓咪的母親」突然告訴了版主貓咪不見了的消息。本來島上有120隻貓，但現在只剩下少於60隻。<br />\n<br />\n即使他們在餵飼場舉行貓貓罐頭派對也好，前來參加的貓咪也只有30隻不到。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/life/catsisland-aoshima-missing/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Flife%2Fcatsisland-aoshima-missing%2F&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7IqQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=64c20791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.likejapan.com/life/catsisland-aoshima-missing/</a>"},{"pid":"28ea33c3e7fb0e2c5a8227092f5bbac5eb14cf6d","tid":2280644,"uid":228894,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T15:24:22.000Z","msg":"希望冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81afefded1c2d698f44562f25ef975a4565a163","tid":2280644,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T15:36:45.000Z","msg":"無人餵餓死晒？<br />\nD屎俾其他貓食埋<br />\n骨就掉晒落海？"},{"pid":"1f6966732a659696da1d759670bf055b29f77d09","tid":2280644,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T22:11:01.000Z","msg":"全個島得5個居民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該唔會有人落毒掛<br />\n可能搭船走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e52d2d1a122de925b382b8db1